e not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"ce49f87172a3fc279521a8fadbddc5b6a4a346b5","tid":1409091,"uid":139729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:33:08.000Z","msg":"罷買美心月餅"},{"pid":"2b0af9d50245bf3e3c6b3ca542b5c8a9be49d110","tid":1409091,"uid":61999,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:33:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>美心你仆街喇今次<br />\n我話嘅</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bb9cda23e0b6e5ececffe0b7c185eeded398ed9f","tid":1409091,"uid":139729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:38:15.000Z","msg":"呼籲罷買美心。<br />\n取消代言人身份"},{"pid":"7a7ecb6198f5720c62670f06d4a0d9ca7b300899","tid":1409091,"uid":139729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:41:23.000Z","msg":"全港罷蝗嘉義代言美心月餅。"},{"pid":"5c7c75434db972288f52959eab222613c8ea254f","tid":1409091,"uid":4562,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"7a7ecb6198f5720c62670f06d4a0d9ca7b300899","tid":1409091,"uid":139729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:41:23.000Z","msg":"全港罷蝗嘉義代言美心月餅。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:42:27.000Z","msg":"岩曬啦有埋張智霖"},{"pid":"8add3267b736e814b828acebfcaba064c2ed6022","tid":1409091,"uid":46314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:45:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee79f0ff4f82d24920a923af6c8d792685c4cdcf","tid":1409091,"uid":64476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:46:44.000Z","msg":"大陸仔"},{"pid":"b83279254e8bd2cd856e16de2da1c090d6782d9c"